{"type":"message","id":"308b8416","parentId":"82f91b6b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:46:01.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating signal scripts**\n\nI need to inspect the existing signal overlay and backtest scripts, along with their data processing. The user wants to start from scratch, so I'll need to create a minimal viable product, like a config file named `day1_mean_reversion.yaml` or `.json`. I'll also write a script called `generate_day1_mean_reversion_signals.py` that reads local data and outputs relevant information.\n\nFirst, I'll check the available data format and the data folder to determine if there's enough data for the project. I should look at one data sample and inspect the `run_stock_analysis_overlay` scripts for the existing interface. Let’s start by reviewing those scripts.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我直接开始落地首版实现：先对齐现有数据格式和信号接入口，再补一个可跑的 day1-3 信号生成脚本。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_DyVmVKYkrOiUw40R2YTrmqsF","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_stock_analysis_overlay_backtest.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_XTjmgyMxzNSyFt3UXpkmvi6b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nroot=Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed')\nfor p in sorted(root.rglob('*.csv'))[:10]:\n    print(p)\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_u8rTj9FIYNnOe8YqpMGgp7om","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\ncands=list(Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data').rglob('*.csv'))\nfor p in cands[:20]:\n    print(p)\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774082745481}}
{"type":"message","id":"71009f85","parentId":"308b8416","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:46:01.110Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_DyVmVKYkrOiUw40R2YTrmqsF","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport json\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nSCRIPTS_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"scripts\"\nfor candidate in [PROJECT_ROOT, SCRIPTS_DIR]:\n    if str(candidate) not in sys.path:\n        sys.path.insert(0, str(candidate))\n\nfrom stock_analysis_decision_bridge import (  # type: ignore\n    DEFAULT_DSA_ROOT,\n    derive_overlay_from_analysis,\n    dsa_runtime_context,\n    normalize_cached_record,\n)\n\nREPORT_DIR = PROJECT_ROOT / \"research\" / \"reports\"\n\n\ndef parse_float(value: Any, default: float = 0.0) -> float:\n    try:\n        return float(str(value).replace(\",\", \"\").strip())\n    except Exception:\n        return default\n\n\ndef compute_group_summary(rows: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    total = len(rows)\n    completed = [row for row in rows if str(row.get(\"eval_status\", \"\")) == \"completed\"]\n    insufficient_count = sum(1 for row in rows if str(row.get(\"eval_status\", \"\")) == \"insufficient_data\")\n    long_count = sum(1 for row in completed if str(row.get(\"position_recommendation\", \"\")) == \"long\")\n    cash_count = sum(1 for row in completed if str(row.get(\"position_recommendation\", \"\")) == \"cash\")\n    win_count = sum(1 for row in completed if str(row.get(\"outcome\", \"\")) == \"win\")\n    loss_count = sum(1 for row in completed if str(row.get(\"outcome\", \"\")) == \"loss\")\n    neutral_count = sum(1 for row in completed if str(row.get(\"outcome\", \"\")) == \"neutral\")\n    direction_rows = [row for row in completed if row.get(\"direction_correct\") is not None]\n    direction_correct = sum(1 for row in direction_rows if row.get(\"direction_correct\") is True)\n    avg_stock_return = (\n        round(sum(parse_float(row.get(\"stock_return_pct\"), 0.0) for row in completed) / len(completed), 4)\n        if completed\n        else None\n    )\n    avg_simulated_return = (\n        round(sum(parse_float(row.get(\"simulated_return_pct\"), 0.0) for row in completed) / len(completed), 4)\n        if completed\n        else None\n    )\n    win_base = win_count + loss_count\n    return {\n        \"total\": total,\n        \"completed_count\": len(completed),\n        \"insufficient_count\": insufficient_count,\n        \"long_count\": long_count,\n        \"cash_count\": cash_count,\n        \"win_count\": win_count,\n        \"loss_count\": loss_count,\n        \"neutral_count\": neutral_count,\n        \"direction_accuracy_pct\": round(direction_correct / len(direction_rows) * 100, 2) if direction_rows else None,\n        \"win_rate_pct\": round(win_count / win_base * 100, 2) if win_base else None,\n        \"avg_stock_return_pct\": avg_stock_return,\n        \"avg_simulated_return_pct\": avg_simulated_return,\n    }\n\n\ndef build_rows(*, eval_window_days: int) -> tuple[list[dict[str, Any]], dict[str, Any]]:\n    with dsa_runtime_context(DEFAULT_DSA_ROOT):\n        from src.config import Config, setup_env  # type: ignore\n        from src.services.backtest_service import BacktestService  # type: ignore\n        from src.storage import AnalysisHistory, BacktestResult, DatabaseManager  # type: ignore\n        from sqlalchemy import and_, select  # type: ignore\n\n        setup_env(override=True)\n        Config.reset_instance()\n        service = BacktestService()\n        run_stats = service.run_backtest(\n            force=False,\n            eval_window_days=eval_window_days,\n            min_age_days=0,\n            limit=500,\n        )\n\n        db = DatabaseManager.get_instance()\n        rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n        with db.get_session() as session:\n            query = (\n                select(AnalysisHistory, BacktestResult)\n                .join(\n                    BacktestResult,\n                    and_(\n                        BacktestResult.analysis_history_id == AnalysisHistory.id,\n                        BacktestResult.eval_window_days == int(eval_window_days),\n                    ),\n                )\n                .order_by(AnalysisHistory.created_at.asc())\n            )\n            for analysis, backtest in session.execute(query).all():\n                analysis_payload = normalize_cached_record(analysis)\n                overlay = derive_overlay_from_analysis(analysis_payload)\n                rows.append(\n                    {\n                        \"analysis_history_id\": analysis.id,\n                        \"code\": analysis_payload.get(\"ts_code\") or analysis.code,\n                        \"stock_name\": analysis_payload.get(\"stock_name\") or analysis.name,\n                        \"created_at\": analysis.created_at.isoformat() if analysis.created_at else \"\",\n                        \"operation_advice\": analysis_payload.get(\"operation_advice\") or analysis.operation_advice,\n                        \"trend_prediction\": analysis_payload.get(\"trend_prediction\"),\n                        \"sentiment_score\": int(parse_float(analysis_payload.get(\"sentiment_score\"), 0.0)),\n                        \"ai_decision\": overlay.get(\"ai_decision\"),\n                        \"ai_budget_scale\": overlay.get(\"ai_budget_scale\"),\n                        \"ai_score_scale\": overlay.get(\"ai_score_scale\"),\n                        \"ai_gate_reason\": overlay.get(\"ai_gate_reason\"),\n                        \"eval_status\": backtest.eval_status,\n                        \"analysis_date\": str(backtest.analysis_date or \"\"),\n                        \"position_recommendation\": backtest.position_recommendation,\n                        \"direction_correct\": backtest.direction_correct,\n                        \"outcome\": backtest.outcome,\n                        \"stock_return_pct\": backtest.stock_return_pct,\n                        \"simulated_return_pct\": backtest.simulated_return_pct,\n                    }\n                )\n        return rows, run_stats\n\n\ndef write_report(path_md: Path, payload: dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    lines = [\n        f\"# 股票分析决策系统分层回测（{payload.get('date_tag', '')}）\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## 结论\",\n        f\"- 评估窗口：`{payload.get('eval_window_days')}` 交易日\",\n        f\"- 总样本：`{payload.get('overall', {}).get('total', 0)}`\",\n        f\"- 已完成：`{payload.get('overall', {}).get('completed_count', 0)}`\",\n        f\"- 数据不足：`{payload.get('overall', {}).get('insufficient_count', 0)}`\",\n        \"- 说明：样本不足时，此结果只用于早期观测，不用于下收益定论。\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## Overall\",\n        f\"- direction_accuracy：`{payload.get('overall', {}).get('direction_accuracy_pct')}`\",\n        f\"- win_rate：`{payload.get('overall', {}).get('win_rate_pct')}`\",\n        f\"- avg_stock_return_pct：`{payload.get('overall', {}).get('avg_stock_return_pct')}`\",\n        f\"- avg_simulated_return_pct：`{payload.get('overall', {}).get('avg_simulated_return_pct')}`\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## 分层结果\",\n        \"\",\n        \"| 决策层 | 总样本 | 已完成 | 数据不足 | 胜率 | 平均标的收益 | 平均模拟收益 |\",\n        \"| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\",\n    ]\n    for name in [\"block\", \"reduce\", \"pass\"]:\n        item = (payload.get(\"groups\") or {}).get(name, {})\n        lines.append(\n            \"| {name} | {total} | {completed} | {insufficient} | {win_rate} | {avg_stock} | {avg_sim} |\".format(\n                name=name,\n                total=item.get(\"total\", 0),\n                completed=item.get(\"completed_count\", 0),\n                insufficient=item.get(\"insufficient_count\", 0),\n                win_rate=item.get(\"win_rate_pct\", \"N/A\"),\n                avg_stock=item.get(\"avg_stock_return_pct\", \"N/A\"),\n                avg_sim=item.get(\"avg_simulated_return_pct\", \"N/A\"),\n            )\n        )\n\n    lines.extend(\n        [\n            \"\",\n            \"## 已完成样本\",\n            \"\",\n            \"| 代码 | 名称 | 建议 | 分层 | 3日标的收益 | 模拟收益 |\",\n            \"| --- | --- | --- | --- | ---: | ---: |\",\n        ]\n    )\n    for row in payload.get(\"rows\", []):\n        if str(row.get(\"eval_status\", \"\")) != \"completed\":\n            continue\n        lines.append(\n            \"| {code} | {name} | {advice} | {decision} | {stock_ret} | {sim_ret} |\".format(\n                code=row.get(\"code\", \"\"),\n                name=row.get(\"stock_name\", \"\"),\n                advice=row.get(\"operation_advice\", \"\"),\n                decision=row.get(\"ai_decision\", \"\"),\n                stock_ret=round(parse_float(row.get(\"stock_return_pct\"), 0.0), 4),\n                sim_ret=round(parse_float(row.get(\"simulated_return_pct\"), 0.0), 4),\n            )\n        )\n    path_md.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    path_md.write_text(\"\\n\".join(lines) + \"\\n\", encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"股票分析决策系统分层回测\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--eval-window-days\", type=int, default=3)\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date-tag\", default=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"))\n    parser.add_argument(\"--output-json\", default=\"\", help=\"默认 research/reports/stock_analysis_overlay_backtest_YYYYMMDD.json\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--output-md\", default=\"\", help=\"默认 research/reports/stock_analysis_overlay_backtest_YYYYMMDD.md\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    rows, run_stats = build_rows(eval_window_days=int(args.eval_window_days))\n    groups: dict[str, list[dict[str, Any]]] = {\"block\": [], \"reduce\": [], \"pass\": []}\n    for row in rows:\n        decision = str(row.get(\"ai_decision\", \"\") or \"\").lower()\n        groups.setdefault(decision, []).append(row)\n\n    payload = {\n        \"generated_at\": datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\"),\n        \"date_tag\": args.date_tag,\n        \"dsa_root\": str(DEFAULT_DSA_ROOT),\n        \"eval_window_days\": int(args.eval_window_days),\n        \"run_stats\": run_stats,\n        \"overall\": compute_group_summary(rows),\n        \"groups\": {name: compute_group_summary(items) for name, items in groups.items()},\n        \"rows\": rows,\n    }\n\n    out_json = Path(args.output_json) if args.output_json else REPORT_DIR / f\"stock_analysis_overlay_backtest_{args.date_tag}.json\"\n    out_md = Path(args.output_md) if args.output_md else REPORT_DIR / f\"stock_analysis_overlay_backtest_{args.date_tag}.md\"\n    out_json.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    out_json.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    write_report(out_md, payload)\n    payload[\"files\"] = {\"json\": str(out_json), \"md\": str(out_md)}\n    print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774082761102}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b7dde3f","parentId":"71009f85","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:46:01.147Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_XTjmgyMxzNSyFt3UXpkmvi6b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/a_stock_history/600000.SH.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000001.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000006.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000010.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000012.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000025.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000030.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000032.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000037.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000048.SZ.csv"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":30,"aggregated":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/a_stock_history/600000.SH.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000001.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000006.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000010.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000012.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000025.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000030.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000032.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000037.SZ.csv\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/qbot_ashare/000048.SZ.csv","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774082761141}}
