{"type":"message","id":"cc5f081d","parentId":"976769f0","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:46:37.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning implementation steps**\n\nI've got enough information to move forward with the implementation. I should inspect merge_signals and explore how to apply risk to signals. It would also be a good idea to think about formatting during this process. Making sure everything is well-structured and easy to read will help in understanding the output when it’s done. Let’s keep that in mind as I dive into the details and start working on this!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我已经定位到现有系统的信号适配模式：先生成候选 CSV，再用 export 脚本写入 `signals/raw/`。下一步我会按这个模式补一个 `day1_3_mean_reversion` 的首版配置和信号生成器。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_B2U6S1j092loRRfUS7lr7JiG","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/merge_signals.py","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9EmG3A9nGuErlhqESteFXKnx","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/apply_risk_to_signals.py","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774082789963}}
{"type":"message","id":"0124e67e","parentId":"cc5f081d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:46:37.574Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_B2U6S1j092loRRfUS7lr7JiG","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Merge multiple standardized signal files into one merged signal output.\n\nv1 规则：\n- 直接合并多份 raw signal\n- 按 trade_date + ts_code + signal_type 聚合\n- 保留 strategy_id 列表\n- score 取平均值\n- target_weight 取平均值\n- comment 合并\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport pandas as pd\n\n\ndef merge_signal_frames(frames: list[pd.DataFrame]) -> pd.DataFrame:\n    if not frames:\n        return pd.DataFrame()\n    df = pd.concat(frames, ignore_index=True)\n    if df.empty:\n        return df\n\n    grouped = (\n        df.groupby([\"trade_date\", \"ts_code\", \"signal_type\"], dropna=False)\n        .agg(\n            score=(\"score\", \"mean\"),\n            target_weight=(\"target_weight\", \"mean\"),\n            strategy_ids=(\"strategy_id\", lambda s: \"|\".join(sorted(set(str(x) for x in s if pd.notna(x))))),\n            risk_flags=(\"risk_flag\", lambda s: \"|\".join(sorted(set(str(x) for x in s if pd.notna(x))))),\n            comments=(\"comment\", lambda s: \" | \".join(str(x) for x in s if pd.notna(x) and str(x).strip())),\n        )\n        .reset_index()\n    )\n    grouped[\"strategy_id\"] = grouped[\"strategy_ids\"]\n    grouped[\"risk_flag\"] = grouped[\"risk_flags\"]\n    grouped[\"comment\"] = grouped[\"comments\"]\n    grouped[\"source_run_id\"] = f\"merged_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')}\"\n    grouped[\"generated_at\"] = datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat()\n    return grouped[[\n        \"trade_date\", \"ts_code\", \"signal_type\", \"score\", \"target_weight\",\n        \"strategy_id\", \"risk_flag\", \"comment\", \"source_run_id\", \"generated_at\"\n    ]]\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    ap = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n    ap.add_argument(\"--inputs\", nargs=\"+\", required=True, help=\"raw signal csv files\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--output\", required=True, help=\"merged output path\")\n    args = ap.parse_args()\n\n    frames = []\n    for p in args.inputs:\n        path = Path(p)\n        if not path.exists():\n            raise FileNotFoundError(path)\n        frames.append(pd.read_csv(path))\n\n    out = merge_signal_frames(frames)\n    output_path = Path(args.output)\n    output_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    out.to_csv(output_path, index=False)\n    print(f\"merged {len(frames)} files -> {len(out)} rows -> {output_path}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Merge multiple standardized signal files into one merged signal output.\n\nv1 规则：\n- 直接合并多份 raw signal\n- 按 trade_date + ts_code + signal_type 聚合\n- 保留 strategy_id 列表\n- score 取平均值\n- target_weight 取平均值\n- comment 合并\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport pandas as pd\n\n\ndef merge_signal_frames(frames: list[pd.DataFrame]) -> pd.DataFrame:\n    if not frames:\n        return pd.DataFrame()\n    df = pd.concat(frames, ignore_index=True)\n    if df.empty:\n        return df\n\n    grouped = (\n        df.groupby([\"trade_date\", \"ts_code\", \"signal_type\"], dropna=False)\n        .agg(\n            score=(\"score\", \"mean\"),\n            target_weight=(\"target_weight\", \"mean\"),\n            strategy_ids=(\"strategy_id\", lambda s: \"|\".join(sorted(set(str(x) for x in s if pd.notna(x))))),\n            risk_flags=(\"risk_flag\", lambda s: \"|\".join(sorted(set(str(x) for x in s if pd.notna(x))))),\n            comments=(\"comment\", lambda s: \" | \".join(str(x) for x in s if pd.notna(x) and str(x).strip())),\n        )\n        .reset_index()\n    )\n    grouped[\"strategy_id\"] = grouped[\"strategy_ids\"]\n    grouped[\"risk_flag\"] = grouped[\"risk_flags\"]\n    grouped[\"comment\"] = grouped[\"comments\"]\n    grouped[\"source_run_id\"] = f\"merged_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')}\"\n    grouped[\"generated_at\"] = datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat()\n    return grouped[[\n        \"trade_date\", \"ts_code\", \"signal_type\", \"score\", \"target_weight\",\n        \"strategy_id\", \"risk_flag\", \"comment\", \"source_run_id\", \"generated_at\"\n    ]]\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    ap = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n    ap.add_argument(\"--inputs\", nargs=\"+\", required=True, help=\"raw signal csv files\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--output\", required=True, help=\"merged output path\")\n    args = ap.parse_args()\n\n    frames = []\n    for p in args.inputs:\n        path = Path(p)\n        if not path.exists():\n            raise FileNotFoundError(path)\n        frames.append(pd.read_csv(path))\n\n    out = merge_signal_frames(frames)\n    output_path = Path(args.output)\n    output_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    out.to_csv(output_path, index=False)\n    print(f\"merged {len(frames)} files -> {len(out)} rows -> {output_path}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774082797568}}
{"type":"message","id":"2aa62910","parentId":"0124e67e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:46:37.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9EmG3A9nGuErlhqESteFXKnx","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Apply risk engine to raw signals and emit approved signals + proposed orders.\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nif str(PROJECT_ROOT) not in sys.path:\n    sys.path.insert(0, str(PROJECT_ROOT))\n\nfrom risk.risk_engine import RiskConfig, RiskContext, RiskEngine\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    ap = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n    ap.add_argument(\"--input\", required=True, help=\"raw signal csv\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--trade-date\", required=True)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--account-nav\", type=float, default=1000000)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--available-cash\", type=float, default=1000000)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--market-breadth\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--index-ret-pct\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--strategy-max-dd-pct\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--strategy-sharpe\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--risk-off\", action=\"store_true\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--hard-stop\", action=\"store_true\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--risk-config\", type=str, default=None, help=\"path to risk config JSON\")\n    args = ap.parse_args()\n\n    base = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\n    input_path = Path(args.input)\n    if not input_path.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(input_path)\n\n    raw = pd.read_csv(input_path)\n\n    if args.risk_config:\n        import json\n        with open(args.risk_config) as f:\n            cfg = json.load(f)\n        risk_config = RiskConfig(\n            max_total_exposure=cfg.get(\"max_total_exposure\", 1.0),\n            max_single_weight=cfg.get(\"max_single_weight\", 0.10),\n            riskoff_total_exposure=cfg.get(\"riskoff_total_exposure\", 0.65),\n            hard_stop_enabled=cfg.get(\"hard_stop_enabled\", True),\n            allow_new_buy_when_riskoff=cfg.get(\"allow_new_buy_when_riskoff\", False),\n            max_order_to_adv20_ratio=cfg.get(\"max_order_to_adv20_ratio\", 0.02),\n            index_halt_threshold_pct=cfg.get(\"index_halt_threshold_pct\"),\n            market_breadth_riskoff_threshold=cfg.get(\"market_breadth_riskoff_threshold\"),\n            market_breadth_hard_stop_threshold=cfg.get(\"market_breadth_hard_stop_threshold\"),\n            strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct=cfg.get(\"strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\"),\n            strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold=cfg.get(\"strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold\"),\n            style_rotation_enabled=cfg.get(\"style_rotation_enabled\", False),\n            style_rotation_riskoff_short_excess_pct=cfg.get(\"style_rotation_riskoff_short_excess_pct\"),\n            style_rotation_riskoff_medium_excess_pct=cfg.get(\"style_rotation_riskoff_medium_excess_pct\"),\n            style_rotation_hard_stop_short_excess_pct=cfg.get(\"style_rotation_hard_stop_short_excess_pct\"),\n            style_rotation_hard_stop_medium_excess_pct=cfg.get(\"style_rotation_hard_stop_medium_excess_pct\"),\n            style_rotation_hard_stop_requires_negative_smallcap=cfg.get(\n                \"style_rotation_hard_stop_requires_negative_smallcap\",\n                True,\n            ),\n            blocked_codes=cfg.get(\"blocked_codes\", []),\n        )\n    else:\n        risk_config = RiskConfig(\n            max_total_exposure=1.0,\n            max_single_weight=0.10,\n            riskoff_total_exposure=0.65,\n            allow_new_buy_when_riskoff=False,\n        )\n\n    engine = RiskEngine(risk_config)\n    context = RiskContext(\n        trade_date=args.trade_date,\n        market_breadth=args.market_breadth,\n        risk_off=args.risk_off,\n        hard_stop=args.hard_stop,\n        available_cash=args.available_cash,\n        account_nav=args.account_nav,\n        index_ret_pct=args.index_ret_pct,\n        strategy_max_drawdown_pct=args.strategy_max_dd_pct,\n        strategy_sharpe=args.strategy_sharpe,\n    )\n\n    approved = engine.apply(raw, context)\n\n    trade_tag = args.trade_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n    approved_path = base / \"signals\" / \"approved\" / f\"approved_signals_{trade_tag}.csv\"\n    approved_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    approved.to_csv(approved_path, index=False)\n\n    # convert to proposed orders: 只保留通过风控的信号\n    if \"approved\" in approved.columns:\n        orders = approved[approved[\"approved\"].fillna(False)].copy()\n    else:\n        orders = approved.copy()\n\n    if \"target_weight\" in orders.columns:\n        orders[\"target_value\"] = orders[\"target_weight\"].fillna(0) * args.account_nav\n    else:\n        buy_rows = max(1, (orders[orders[\"signal_type\"] == \"BUY\"][\"ts_code\"].nunique() or 1))\n        default_value = args.available_cash / buy_rows\n        orders[\"target_value\"] = orders[\"signal_type\"].map(lambda x: default_value if x == \"BUY\" else 0)\n\n    orders[\"action\"] = orders[\"signal_type\"]\n    orders[\"reason\"] = orders.get(\"comment\", \"\")\n    orders[\"generated_at\"] = datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat()\n    orders[\"source_signal_file\"] = str(input_path)\n\n    keep_cols = [\n        \"trade_date\", \"ts_code\", \"action\", \"target_value\", \"target_weight\",\n        \"strategy_id\", \"score\", \"risk_adjustment\", \"risk_status\", \"reason\",\n        \"source_signal_file\", \"generated_at\", \"approved\",\n    ]\n    for col in keep_cols:\n        if col not in orders.columns:\n            orders[col] = None\n    orders = orders[keep_cols]\n\n    proposed_path = base / \"orders\" / \"proposed\" / f\"proposed_orders_{trade_tag}.csv\"\n    proposed_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    orders.to_csv(proposed_path, index=False)\n\n    print(f\"approved signals -> {approved_path}\")\n    print(f\"proposed orders -> {proposed_path}\")\n    approved_true = int(approved[\"approved\"].fillna(False).sum()) if \"approved\" in approved.columns else len(approved)\n    print(f\"rows: total={len(approved)}, approved={approved_true}, orders={len(orders)}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Apply risk engine to raw signals and emit approved signals + proposed orders.\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport pandas as pd\n\nPROJECT_ROOT = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\nif str(PROJECT_ROOT) not in sys.path:\n    sys.path.insert(0, str(PROJECT_ROOT))\n\nfrom risk.risk_engine import RiskConfig, RiskContext, RiskEngine\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    ap = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n    ap.add_argument(\"--input\", required=True, help=\"raw signal csv\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--trade-date\", required=True)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--account-nav\", type=float, default=1000000)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--available-cash\", type=float, default=1000000)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--market-breadth\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--index-ret-pct\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--strategy-max-dd-pct\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--strategy-sharpe\", type=float, default=None)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--risk-off\", action=\"store_true\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--hard-stop\", action=\"store_true\")\n    ap.add_argument(\"--risk-config\", type=str, default=None, help=\"path to risk config JSON\")\n    args = ap.parse_args()\n\n    base = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\n    input_path = Path(args.input)\n    if not input_path.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(input_path)\n\n    raw = pd.read_