{"type":"message","id":"d096bd84","parentId":"b7f9ef5e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:49:05.258Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning coding tasks**\n\nI need to continue with the task and implement some scripts and configurations, plus conduct a smoke test. I think using active_task_cli for transitions could be beneficial, but we can manage without that until the deliverable is ready. Editing files in the quant project and committing them is next on my list. I wonder if I should use a skill coding-agent. It seems like I can handle the coding myself, but it may be worth reading more about the expected inputs. Also, I'll need to create the necessary configuration and script while checking relevant sources to ensure everything’s set.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_LJYJ4shFNMAGr6eEcxlRaKSY","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '220,420p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_rd_agent_factor_overlay_backtest.py","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_v6JbOR2B7lzolO9naeCviuNQ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -R \"strategy_smallcap_chip\" -n /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/README.md /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/docs /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports | head -20","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774082935360}}
{"type":"message","id":"39032bef","parentId":"d096bd84","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:49:05.331Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_LJYJ4shFNMAGr6eEcxlRaKSY","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"parser.add_argument(\"--rd-file\", default=\"\", help=\"显式指定RD因子文件（CSV）\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--tag\", default=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"), help=\"输出标签\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--check-only\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"只校验接入与覆盖率，不跑Qlib回测\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    config_path = (PROJECT_ROOT / args.config).resolve() if not Path(args.config).is_absolute() else Path(args.config)\n    cfg = load_yaml(config_path)\n\n    if not bool(cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)):\n        print(json.dumps({\"status\": \"DISABLED\", \"config\": str(config_path)}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    source_cfg = cfg.get(\"source\", {})\n    blend_cfg = cfg.get(\"blend\", {})\n    bt_cfg = cfg.get(\"backtest\", {})\n\n    source_dir = Path(source_cfg.get(\"root_dir\", \"\")).expanduser()\n    pattern = str(source_cfg.get(\"glob_pattern\", \"*.csv\"))\n\n    rd_file = Path(args.rd_file).expanduser() if args.rd_file else discover_latest_factor_file(source_dir, pattern)\n\n    if rd_file is None or not rd_file.exists():\n        payload = write_waiting_report(tag=args.tag, config_path=config_path, source_dir=source_dir)\n        print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    rd_signal, rd_meta = load_rd_factor_series(\n        file_path=rd_file,\n        date_col=str(source_cfg.get(\"date_col\", \"date\")),\n        symbol_col=str(source_cfg.get(\"symbol_col\", \"instrument\")),\n        score_col=str(source_cfg.get(\"score_col\", \"score\")),\n        encoding=str(source_cfg.get(\"encoding\", \"utf-8\")),\n    )\n\n    REPORT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n\n    if args.check_only:\n        preview = rd_signal.reset_index().rename(columns={\"datetime\": \"date\", \"instrument\": \"symbol\"}).head(50)\n        preview_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_factor_preview_{args.tag}.csv\"\n        preview.to_csv(preview_path, index=False)\n\n        payload = {\n            \"generated_at\": timestamp,\n            \"status\": \"CHECK_OK\",\n            \"config\": str(config_path),\n            \"rd_factor_file\": str(rd_file),\n            \"rd_meta\": rd_meta,\n            \"files\": {\"preview\": str(preview_path)},\n        }\n        out = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_integration_check_{args.tag}.json\"\n        out.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n        print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    # 1) 基线信号\n    breadth = sanity.load_market_breadth()\n    pred, start_date, end_date = sanity.train_prediction()\n    base_signal = sanity.shift_signal_one_day(pred)\n\n    # 2) 融合信号\n    base_weight = float(blend_cfg.get(\"base_weight\", 0.75))\n    rd_weight = float(blend_cfg.get(\"rd_weight\", 0.25))\n    fill_missing = float(blend_cfg.get(\"fill_missing_rd_score\", 0.0))\n\n    blended_signal, merged_df, coverage_stats = build_blended_signal(\n        base_signal=base_signal,\n        rd_signal=rd_signal,\n        base_weight=base_weight,\n        rd_weight=rd_weight,\n        fill_missing_rd_score=fill_missing,\n    )\n\n    # 3) 同参数回测对比\n    profile = bt_cfg.get(\"breadth_profile\", {})\n    base_result = sanity.run_backtest_once(\n        pred_shifted=base_signal,\n        start_date=start_date,\n        end_date=end_date,\n        breadth=breadth,\n        topk=int(bt_cfg.get(\"topk\", 10)),\n        n_drop=int(bt_cfg.get(\"n_drop\", 1)),\n        hold_thresh=int(bt_cfg.get(\"hold_thresh\", 4)),\n        risk_degree=float(bt_cfg.get(\"risk_degree\", 0.5)),\n        profile={\n            \"low_th\": float(profile.get(\"low_th\", 0.48)),\n            \"mid_th\": float(profile.get(\"mid_th\", 0.55)),\n            \"low_scale\": float(profile.get(\"low_scale\", 0.30)),\n            \"mid_scale\": float(profile.get(\"mid_scale\", 0.60)),\n            \"high_scale\": float(profile.get(\"high_scale\", 0.95)),\n        },\n    )\n\n    blended_result = sanity.run_backtest_once(\n        pred_shifted=blended_signal,\n        start_date=start_date,\n        end_date=end_date,\n        breadth=breadth,\n        topk=int(bt_cfg.get(\"topk\", 10)),\n        n_drop=int(bt_cfg.get(\"n_drop\", 1)),\n        hold_thresh=int(bt_cfg.get(\"hold_thresh\", 4)),\n        risk_degree=float(bt_cfg.get(\"risk_degree\", 0.5)),\n        profile={\n            \"low_th\": float(profile.get(\"low_th\", 0.48)),\n            \"mid_th\": float(profile.get(\"mid_th\", 0.55)),\n            \"low_scale\": float(profile.get(\"low_scale\", 0.30)),\n            \"mid_scale\": float(profile.get(\"mid_scale\", 0.60)),\n            \"high_scale\": float(profile.get(\"high_scale\", 0.95)),\n        },\n    )\n\n    # 4) 输出\n    signal_out = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_overlay_signal_{args.tag}.csv\"\n    out_df = merged_df.reset_index().rename(columns={\"datetime\": \"date\", \"instrument\": \"symbol\"})\n    out_df.to_csv(signal_out, index=False)\n\n    base_result = to_serializable(base_result)\n    blended_result = to_serializable(blended_result)\n\n    compare = {\n        \"annual_return_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(blended_result.get(\"annual_return_pct\", 0.0) - base_result.get(\"annual_return_pct\", 0.0)), 2\n        ),\n        \"max_drawdown_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(blended_result.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0) - base_result.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0)), 2\n        ),\n        \"sharpe_delta\": round(float(blended_result.get(\"sharpe\", 0.0) - base_result.get(\"sharpe\", 0.0)), 3),\n        \"recent_annual_return_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(\n                blended_result.get(\"recent_annual_return_pct\", 0.0)\n                - base_result.get(\"recent_annual_return_pct\", 0.0)\n            ),\n            2,\n        ),\n        \"recent_max_drawdown_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(\n                blended_result.get(\"recent_max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0)\n                - base_result.get(\"recent_max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0)\n            ),\n            2,\n        ),\n    }\n\n    payload = {\n        \"generated_at\": timestamp,\n        \"status\": \"DONE\",\n        \"config\": str(config_path),\n        \"rd_factor_file\": str(rd_file),\n        \"rd_meta\": rd_meta,\n        \"coverage\": coverage_stats,\n        \"blend_weights\": {\n            \"base_weight\": base_weight,\n            \"rd_weight\": rd_weight,\n            \"fill_missing_rd_score\": fill_missing,\n        },\n        \"base_result\": base_result,\n        \"rd_overlay_result\": blended_result,\n        \"comparison\": compare,\n        \"files\": {\"overlay_signal\": str(signal_out)},\n    }\n\n    json_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_overlay_backtest_{args.tag}.json\"\n    md_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_overlay_backtest_{args.tag}.md\"\n\n    json_path.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    lines = [\n        f\"# RD-Agent 因子融合回测（{args.tag}）\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"- 生成时间：{timestamp}\",\n        f\"- RD因子文件：`{rd_file}`\",\n        f\"- 覆盖率：{coverage_stats['coverage_ratio']:.2%}\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## 基线 vs 融合（同参数）\",\n        \"\",\n        \"| 指标 | 基线 | 融合后 | 变化 |\",\n        \"|---|---:|---:|---:|\",\n        f\"| 年化收益(%) | {base_result.get('annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['annual_return_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        f\"| 最大回撤(%) | {base_result.get('max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['max_drawdown_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        f\"| 夏普 | {base_result.get('sharpe', 0):.3f} | {blended_result.get('sharpe', 0):.3f} | {compare['sharpe_delta']:+.3f} |\",\n        f\"| 近段年化(%) | {base_result.get('recent_annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('recent_annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['recent_annual_return_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        f\"| 近段回撤(%) | {base_result.get('recent_max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('recent_max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['recent_max_drawdown_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## 输出文件\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"- JSON：`{json_path}`\",\n        f\"- 融合信号：`{signal_out}`\",\n    ]\n    md_path.write_text(\"\\n\".join(lines), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    payload[\"files\"][\"json\"] = str(json_path)\n    payload[\"files\"][\"md\"] = str(md_path)\n\n    print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"parser.add_argument(\"--rd-file\", default=\"\", help=\"显式指定RD因子文件（CSV）\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--tag\", default=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\"), help=\"输出标签\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--check-only\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"只校验接入与覆盖率，不跑Qlib回测\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    config_path = (PROJECT_ROOT / args.config).resolve() if not Path(args.config).is_absolute() else Path(args.config)\n    cfg = load_yaml(config_path)\n\n    if not bool(cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)):\n        print(json.dumps({\"status\": \"DISABLED\", \"config\": str(config_path)}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    source_cfg = cfg.get(\"source\", {})\n    blend_cfg = cfg.get(\"blend\", {})\n    bt_cfg = cfg.get(\"backtest\", {})\n\n    source_dir = Path(source_cfg.get(\"root_dir\", \"\")).expanduser()\n    pattern = str(source_cfg.get(\"glob_pattern\", \"*.csv\"))\n\n    rd_file = Path(args.rd_file).expanduser() if args.rd_file else discover_latest_factor_file(source_dir, pattern)\n\n    if rd_file is None or not rd_file.exists():\n        payload = write_waiting_report(tag=args.tag, config_path=config_path, source_dir=source_dir)\n        print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    rd_signal, rd_meta = load_rd_factor_series(\n        file_path=rd_file,\n        date_col=str(source_cfg.get(\"date_col\", \"date\")),\n        symbol_col=str(source_cfg.get(\"symbol_col\", \"instrument\")),\n        score_col=str(source_cfg.get(\"score_col\", \"score\")),\n        encoding=str(source_cfg.get(\"encoding\", \"utf-8\")),\n    )\n\n    REPORT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n\n    if args.check_only:\n        preview = rd_signal.reset_index().rename(columns={\"datetime\": \"date\", \"instrument\": \"symbol\"}).head(50)\n        preview_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_factor_preview_{args.tag}.csv\"\n        preview.to_csv(preview_path, index=False)\n\n        payload = {\n            \"generated_at\": timestamp,\n            \"status\": \"CHECK_OK\",\n            \"config\": str(config_path),\n            \"rd_factor_file\": str(rd_file),\n            \"rd_meta\": rd_meta,\n            \"files\": {\"preview\": str(preview_path)},\n        }\n        out = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_integration_check_{args.tag}.json\"\n        out.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n        print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n\n    # 1) 基线信号\n    breadth = sanity.load_market_breadth()\n    pred, start_date, end_date = sanity.train_prediction()\n    base_signal = sanity.shift_signal_one_day(pred)\n\n    # 2) 融合信号\n    base_weight = float(blend_cfg.get(\"base_weight\", 0.75))\n    rd_weight = float(blend_cfg.get(\"rd_weight\", 0.25))\n    fill_missing = float(blend_cfg.get(\"fill_missing_rd_score\", 0.0))\n\n    blended_signal, merged_df, coverage_stats = build_blended_signal(\n        base_signal=base_signal,\n        rd_signal=rd_signal,\n        base_weight=base_weight,\n        rd_weight=rd_weight,\n        fill_missing_rd_score=fill_missing,\n    )\n\n    # 3) 同参数回测对比\n    profile = bt_cfg.get(\"breadth_profile\", {})\n    base_result = sanity.run_backtest_once(\n        pred_shifted=base_signal,\n        start_date=start_date,\n        end_date=end_date,\n        breadth=breadth,\n        topk=int(bt_cfg.get(\"topk\", 10)),\n        n_drop=int(bt_cfg.get(\"n_drop\", 1)),\n        hold_thresh=int(bt_cfg.get(\"hold_thresh\", 4)),\n        risk_degree=float(bt_cfg.get(\"risk_degree\", 0.5)),\n        profile={\n            \"low_th\": float(profile.get(\"low_th\", 0.48)),\n            \"mid_th\": float(profile.get(\"mid_th\", 0.55)),\n            \"low_scale\": float(profile.get(\"low_scale\", 0.30)),\n            \"mid_scale\": float(profile.get(\"mid_scale\", 0.60)),\n            \"high_scale\": float(profile.get(\"high_scale\", 0.95)),\n        },\n    )\n\n    blended_result = sanity.run_backtest_once(\n        pred_shifted=blended_signal,\n        start_date=start_date,\n        end_date=end_date,\n        breadth=breadth,\n        topk=int(bt_cfg.get(\"topk\", 10)),\n        n_drop=int(bt_cfg.get(\"n_drop\", 1)),\n        hold_thresh=int(bt_cfg.get(\"hold_thresh\", 4)),\n        risk_degree=float(bt_cfg.get(\"risk_degree\", 0.5)),\n        profile={\n            \"low_th\": float(profile.get(\"low_th\", 0.48)),\n            \"mid_th\": float(profile.get(\"mid_th\", 0.55)),\n            \"low_scale\": float(profile.get(\"low_scale\", 0.30)),\n            \"mid_scale\": float(profile.get(\"mid_scale\", 0.60)),\n            \"high_scale\": float(profile.get(\"high_scale\", 0.95)),\n        },\n    )\n\n    # 4) 输出\n    signal_out = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_overlay_signal_{args.tag}.csv\"\n    out_df = merged_df.reset_index().rename(columns={\"datetime\": \"date\", \"instrument\": \"symbol\"})\n    out_df.to_csv(signal_out, index=False)\n\n    base_result = to_serializable(base_result)\n    blended_result = to_serializable(blended_result)\n\n    compare = {\n        \"annual_return_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(blended_result.get(\"annual_return_pct\", 0.0) - base_result.get(\"annual_return_pct\", 0.0)), 2\n        ),\n        \"max_drawdown_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(blended_result.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0) - base_result.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0)), 2\n        ),\n        \"sharpe_delta\": round(float(blended_result.get(\"sharpe\", 0.0) - base_result.get(\"sharpe\", 0.0)), 3),\n        \"recent_annual_return_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(\n                blended_result.get(\"recent_annual_return_pct\", 0.0)\n                - base_result.get(\"recent_annual_return_pct\", 0.0)\n            ),\n            2,\n        ),\n        \"recent_max_drawdown_pct_delta\": round(\n            float(\n                blended_result.get(\"recent_max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0)\n                - base_result.get(\"recent_max_drawdown_pct\", 0.0)\n            ),\n            2,\n        ),\n    }\n\n    payload = {\n        \"generated_at\": timestamp,\n        \"status\": \"DONE\",\n        \"config\": str(config_path),\n        \"rd_factor_file\": str(rd_file),\n        \"rd_meta\": rd_meta,\n        \"coverage\": coverage_stats,\n        \"blend_weights\": {\n            \"base_weight\": base_weight,\n            \"rd_weight\": rd_weight,\n            \"fill_missing_rd_score\": fill_missing,\n        },\n        \"base_result\": base_result,\n        \"rd_overlay_result\": blended_result,\n        \"comparison\": compare,\n        \"files\": {\"overlay_signal\": str(signal_out)},\n    }\n\n    json_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_overlay_backtest_{args.tag}.json\"\n    md_path = REPORT_DIR / f\"rd_agent_overlay_backtest_{args.tag}.md\"\n\n    json_path.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    lines = [\n        f\"# RD-Agent 因子融合回测（{args.tag}）\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"- 生成时间：{timestamp}\",\n        f\"- RD因子文件：`{rd_file}`\",\n        f\"- 覆盖率：{coverage_stats['coverage_ratio']:.2%}\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## 基线 vs 融合（同参数）\",\n        \"\",\n        \"| 指标 | 基线 | 融合后 | 变化 |\",\n        \"|---|---:|---:|---:|\",\n        f\"| 年化收益(%) | {base_result.get('annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['annual_return_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        f\"| 最大回撤(%) | {base_result.get('max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['max_drawdown_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        f\"| 夏普 | {base_result.get('sharpe', 0):.3f} | {blended_result.get('sharpe', 0):.3f} | {compare['sharpe_delta']:+.3f} |\",\n        f\"| 近段年化(%) | {base_result.get('recent_annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('recent_annual_return_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['recent_annual_return_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        f\"| 近段回撤(%) | {base_result.get('recent_max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {blended_result.get('recent_max_drawdown_pct', 0):.2f} | {compare['recent_max_drawdown_pct_delta']:+.2f} |\",\n        \"\",\n        \"## 输出文件\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"- JSON：`{json_path}`\",\n        f\"- 融合信号：`{signal_out}`\",\n    ]\n    md_path.write_text(\"\\n\".join(lines), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n    payload[\"files\"][\"json\"] = str(json_path)\n    payload[\"files\"][\"md\"] = str(md_path)\n\n    print(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774082945323}}
