{"type":"message","id":"ed7e64fc","parentId":"ae0e7314","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:07:54.752Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The commit was successful. The commit hash is 0e5a86d. Now I should report to the user what was accomplished. Let me also check the generated files to provide a summary.","thinkingSignature":"ce091444d76f94f07f6f29e3c0f857d0992ca252f5a01b97ba10317e50aa88fa"},{"type":"text","text":"首版 day1-3 均值回归策略已经实现并通过最小验收！\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 已完成\n\n### 1. 配置文件\n- `config/day1_3_mean_reversion.yaml` - 策略参数配置（信号过滤条件、权重、市场门控）\n- `config/rd_agent_integration_day1_3.yaml` - RD 因子接入配置\n\n### 2. 信号生成脚本\n- `scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py` - 完整的日频均值回归信号生成器\n\n### 3. Smoke Test 结果 (2026-03-10)\n```json\n{\n  \"trade_date\": \"2026-03-10\",\n  \"market_regime\": \"neutral\",\n  \"index_trend\": -0.0019,\n  \"exposure_scale\": 0.6,\n  \"candidates\": 12,\n  \"total_weight\": 43.20%,\n  \"top3\": [\n    {\"ts_code\": \"002039.SZ\", \"score\": 0.475, \"weight\": 3.61%},\n    {\"ts_code\": \"688311.SH\", \"score\": 0.475, \"weight\": 3.60%},\n    {\"ts_code\": \"688590.SH\", \"score\": 0.475, \"weight\": 3.60%}\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 4. 输出文件\n| 文件 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| 候选股 | `research/reports/day1_3_candidates_20260310.csv` |\n| RD因子 | `data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv` |\n| 原始信号 | `signals/raw/day1_3_mean_reversion_20260310.csv` |\n\n---\n\n## 📌 下一步建议\n\n1. **调优参数** - 当前过滤条件较宽松，可收紧（如 max_ret5 从 5% 降到 -2%）\n2. **增加超额收益过滤** - 对标 HS300 的超额收益筛选\n3. **Walk-Forward 验证** - 用 `run_walk_forward.py` 验证策略在更长周期是否稳健\n4. **融合回测** - 用 RD agent overlay 测试与现有策略的叠加效果\n\n**Commit**: `0e5a86d`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":96820,"output":532,"cacheRead":24928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122280,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774084050464}}
