{"type":"message","id":"705c9a47","parentId":"810c8bb8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:22:12.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the current task is cleared. The optimization is done. Let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"fad51ea253a06b0a202359d966a7fde5913a0da286dd5ec90e5d9bc7e447261d"},{"type":"text","text":"day1-3 策略优化完成！\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 优化完成\n\n### 修复的问题\n1. **Rolling MA 计算 bug**：原来在单日数据上计算 rolling 导致全部 NaN，改为先在全量历史计算再筛选当日\n2. **收紧过滤条件**：\n   - `max_ret5`: 5% → **-1%**（只选下跌的）\n   - `max_dist_ma10`: 10% → **-0.5%**（只选低于均线的）\n   - `max_range_pos20`: 80% → **55%**（只选低位区间）\n   - `min_amount`: 10万 → **300万**（提升流动性）\n\n### 优化后的候选股 (2026-03-10)\n| 排名 | 代码 | 收盘价 | 5日跌幅 | 偏离MA10 | 仓位 |\n|------|------|--------|---------|----------|------|\n| 1 | 300164.SZ | 18.90 | -12.9% | -1.38% | 4.91% |\n| 2 | 300308.SZ | 547.0 | -2.98% | -0.93% | 4.42% |\n| 3 | 600183.SH | 64.41 | -4.78% | -3.66% | 4.34% |\n| 4 | 601600.SH | 13.70 | -1.93% | -2.06% | 4.30% |\n| 5 | 300757.SZ | 390.16 | -10.3% | -3.08% | 4.19% |\n\n---\n\n## 📌 下一步可选\n\n1. **Walk-Forward 验证** - 拉长回测周期到 2020-2026 验证策略稳健性\n2. **融合回测** - 用 RD agent overlay 测试与现有策略叠加效果\n3. **市场宽度改进** - 当前 neutral/strong/weak 判断较简化，可接入真实市场宽度数据\n\n**Commit**: `56fda8c`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60356,"output":475,"cacheRead":26949,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774084906146}}
