{"type":"message","id":"afa5b958","parentId":"c6501545","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:32:03.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me summarize the improvements to the user.","thinkingSignature":"db77f19478717b8075c0484fc9365b9d5113176b05809dbb643567bc292de7f9"},{"type":"text","text":"市场宽度计算优化完成！\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 改进完成\n\n### 新增：真实市场宽度计算\n- **之前**：使用固定值 breadth=0.5\n- **现在**：计算当日实际有多少股票收盘价高于其20日均线\n\n### 2026-03-10 实际计算结果\n| 指标 | 值 | 判断 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| 市场宽度 | **48.56%** | 中性区间 (48%-58%) |\n| HS300 趋势 | -0.19% | 略偏负 |\n| 市场状态 | **neutral** | 仓位系数 0.6 |\n\n### 判断逻辑\n```\nstrong: breadth ≥ 58% AND trend ≥ 0\nneutral: breadth ≥ 48% AND trend ≥ -3%  \nweak: 其他情况 → 仓位系数 0.3\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 当前 day1-3 策略状态\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 超跌信号 | ✅ ret5≤-1%, dist_ma10≤-0.5%, range_pos20≤55% |\n| 市场门控 | ✅ 真实市场宽度 + HS300 趋势 |\n| 候选股数 | 12只 (neutral模式) |\n| 总仓位 | 43.20% × 0.6 = **25.92%** |\n\n---\n\n**Commit**: `70448c9`\n\n继续优化还是先验证策略效果？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":67083,"output":316,"cacheRead":26949,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94348,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774085508130}}
