{"type":"message","id":"154347b2","parentId":"b305c484","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:35:46.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task is now complete. Let me summarize the optimization progress for the user.","thinkingSignature":"c8ded6962f7efaacaf9d14eecbd3910f13df4d769576fef163c6cefb7ba7dafe"},{"type":"text","text":"超额收益过滤优化完成！\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 超额收益过滤已实现\n\n### 新增特征：excess_ret5 (相对HS300超额收益)\n- 计算公式：`excess_ret5 = stock_ret5 - hs300_ret5`\n- 筛选条件：`excess_ret5 ≤ -1%`（跑输大盘）\n\n### 2026-03-10 候选股分析\n| 代码 | 5日跌幅 | 相对HS300超额 | 评分 |\n|------|---------|---------------|------|\n| 300164.SZ | -12.9% | **-13.3%** | 2.29 |\n| 300308.SZ | -3.0% | **-3.4%** | 2.17 |\n| 600183.SH | -4.8% | **-5.2%** | 2.08 |\n| 600028.SH | -16.1% | **-16.5%** | 1.38 |\n\n**所有12只候选股的excess_ret5均为负值**，说明策略成功筛选出相对大盘超跌的股票。\n\n---\n\n## 📊 当前策略完整特征\n\n| 特征 | 过滤条件 | 权重 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| ret5 (5日跌幅) | ≤ -1% | 25% |\n| excess_ret5 (相对HS300) | ≤ -1% | 20% |\n| dist_ma10 (偏离均线) | ≤ -0.5% | 30% |\n| range_pos20 (20日低位) | ≤ 55% | 15% |\n| reversal_bar (当日反弹) | 可选 | 10% |\n\n---\n\n**Commit**: `b3312e4`\n\n继续优化还是验证策略效果？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":77184,"output":392,"cacheRead":26949,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104525,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774085737363}}
