{"type":"message","id":"6ebe7224","parentId":"8246bd00","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:19:33.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! The results show:- The coverage is 0% because we only have ONE day of day1-3 factor data (2026-03-10)- The overlay didn't change anything because the day1-3 factor only covered 3 symbols for 1 day- The base and overlay results are identical (delta = 0)The issue is that we need MORE historical day1-3 factor data for the fusion to work properly. The current factor file only has 3 rows for 1 day.\n\nFor Walk-Forward validation, we'd need to:1. Generate day1-3 signals for multiple dates (e.g., every week for 2020-2026)2. Run the overlay backtest with that historical data\n\nThis is a significant task. Let me explain the situation to the user and ask if they want to:1. Generate more historical signals (would take time)\n2. Or just note this limitation for nowSince the user wants to continue, let me at least commit what we have and explain the situation.","thinkingSignature":"5945636903761dd10dc62a8fa4b633b040a6857e5c5fe2b14f187799c1b268b3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jyudvsg2kbc1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git add quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/rd_agent_overlay_backtest_day1_3_v1.json quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/day1_3_mean_reversion.yaml && git commit -m \"test(day1-3): run fusion backtest with RD agent overlay\n\n- Run overlay backtest with day1-3 factor\n- Result: coverage=0% because only 1 day of factor data (3 symbols)\n- Need historical factor generation for proper fusion backtest\"","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":95324,"output":372,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137104,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","tim