{"type":"message","id":"5cd8491f","parentId":"e37dee6e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:19:45.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me explain the situation to the user:","thinkingSignature":"d177e62b34de03c30eca1fc8d82809ce88b65899991503def7bee5c250575ce2"},{"type":"text","text":"融合回测完成，但发现一个关键问题：\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 当前限制\n\n### 融合回测结果\n| 指标 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| 年化收益 | 38.32% |\n| 最大回撤 | 19.22% |\n| 夏普 | 1.562 |\n| **RD因子覆盖** | **0%** |\n\n### 问题原因\n当前 day1-3 因子文件**只有1天数据**（2026-03-10，3只股票），无法影响长期回测结果。\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 需要补充\n\n要实现真正的融合回测，需要：\n\n1. **生成历史因子** - 跑多年数据（2020-2026）每周生成 day1-3 信号\n2. **累积CSV** - 合并成 `day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_history.csv`\n3. **重新回测** - 用历史因子做 overlay\n\n---\n\n## 📊 基础策略现状（已有）\n\n现有系统（不依赖 day1-3）：\n- 年化收益：**38.32%**\n- 最大回撤：**19.22%**\n- 夏普：**1.562**\n\n---\n\n是否需要我生成历史因子数据来进行完整的融合验证？（预计需要较长时间）\n\n**Commit**: `f645914`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":96165,"output":283,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137856,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774088377675}}
