{"type":"message","id":"bcae21bb","parentId":"3e6d8d04","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:27:28.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The fusion backtest is complete with real historical factor data. Let me analyze the results:\n\n- Base result (without day1-3): 38.32% annual return, 19.22% max drawdown, 1.562 sharpe\n- With day1-3 overlay: 37.26% annual return, 19.22% max drawdown, 1.523 sharpe\n\nThe delta:\n- annual_return_pct_delta: -1.06% (slightly lower)\n- sharpe_delta: -0.039 (slightly lower)\n- max_drawdown_pct_delta: 0.0 (same)\n- recent_annual_return_pct_delta: -3.27%This suggests that:\n1. The day1-3 factor has slight negative contribution in this period2. But the max drawdown didn't increase3. The strategy is reasonably stableLet me check the coverage to see how much the factor actually contributed.","thinkingSignature":"8bc65a80d1a405a80c6a2e9a454de0c67673e2389b7fe172a7a7004a638dbe69"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g63nibtkq06x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/rd_agent_overlay_backtest_day1_3_history.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print('Coverage:', d['coverage'])\"","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":102705,"output":306,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144419,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774088840470}}
