{"type":"message","id":"5d775abf","parentId":"f33a5e0c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:27:42.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The coverage is very low (0.11%) because:\n1. We only have ~30 days of factor data (about 1.5 months)\n2. Each day only has 3-12 stocks\n3. The backtest runs on much longer period (years)\n\nSo the factor impact is minimal in this test. To get meaningful results, we'd need:\n1. More historical factor data (at least 1-2 years)\n2. Or run the backtest only on the overlapping period\n\nBut the test shows the infrastructure works. Let me commit the results and summarize.","thinkingSignature":"f6cc7d4b0b56715c6627985d8cb968a40bcde064af2031edd003721a9acd0b71"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zbbpijsefyku_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git add quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/rd_agent_integration_day1_3.yaml quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_history.csv quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/signals/raw/day1_3_mean_reversion_2026*.csv quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/rd_agent_overlay_backtest_day1_3_history.json && git commit -m \"test(day1-3): generate historical factors and run fusion backtest\n\n- Generate 30 days of day1-3 signals (2026-01-29 to 2026-03-19)\n- Combine into history factor CSV (243 rows, 64 symbols)\n- Run fusion backtest:\n  - Base: 38.32% ann, 19.22% dd, 1.562 sharpe\n  - Overlay: 37.26% ann, 19.22% dd, 1.523 sharpe\n  - Delta: -1.06% ann, 0% dd, -0.039 sharpe\n- Note: coverage only 0.11% due to limited factor history\"","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":103103,"output":424,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144935,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timest