{"type":"message","id":"3b6465b6","parentId":"a5a24cae","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:54:10.790Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So it works for 2024! The background batch must have failed silently for some dates. Let me run the full generation again but more carefully. Actually, it seems like only 30 days (the tail) were generated because we specified dates from 2024, but only the latest ones got processed.\n\nActually, wait - looking at the log output, it said \"Processing batch 1/11\" through \"Processing batch 11/11\" and \"Done generating factors!\" - so it seems like it did process all batches. But the files weren't saved. Let me check if maybe the background process didn't have the right working directory or something. Let me try a simpler approach - generate all the dates in a single loop directly.","thinkingSignature":"799a68b4bde3ba3c6ce0cd9a1f2331c4a629f61f922a516e91646a5c3d46f0bc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a7gtg3id4u69_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && python3 - <<'PY'\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport subprocess\n\n# Get dates\nhist_path = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/data/a_stock_history.csv')\ndates = pd.read_csv(hist_path, usecols=['trade_date'], dtype={'trade_date': str})\ndates = dates['trade_date'].drop_duplicates().sort_values()\ndates = dates[(dates >= '20240101') & (dates <= '20260319')]\nformatted = [f\"{d[:4]}-{d[4:6]}-{d[6:]}\" for d in dates.tolist()]\n\nprint(f\"Total dates to process: {len(formatted)}\")\n\n# Process each date\nscript = Path(\"scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py\")\ncount = 0\nfor i, d in enumerate(formatted):\n    result = subprocess.run(\n        [\"python3\", str(script), \"--trade-date\", d],\n        capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=60\n    )\n    if result.returncode == 0:\n        count += 1\n    if (i+1) % 50 == 0:\n        print(f\"Processed {i+1}/{len(formatted)} dates...\")\n\nprint(f\"Successfully generated {count} days of factors\")\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","background":true,"timeout":3600}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117374,"output":498,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":159280,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774090438172}}
