{"type":"message","id":"53b80bf0","parentId":"80bde0ec","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:01:57.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The coverage is still low (0.11%). This is because the day1-3 factor only has signals on certain days (when oversold conditions are met), not every day. The backtest engine might be looking at daily coverage differently.\n\nLet me summarize for the user what we've accomplished with the daily_stock_analysis (day1-3) integration.","thinkingSignature":"4331dbe4e79b725cd5596b66772063adf5ddb57efc7aaf8eff05da4d13664433"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 day1-3 融合进展汇报\n\n### 已完成\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 信号生成脚本 | ✅ `generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py` |\n| 历史因子数据 | ✅ **936行**，覆盖 **115只股票**（2024-01 ~ 2026-03） |\n| 融合配置 | ✅ `rd_agent_integration_day1_3.yaml` |\n| 融合回测 | ✅ 已执行 |\n\n### 回测结果对比\n\n| 指标 | 基础策略 | +day1-3融合 | 变化 |\n|------|----------|--------------|------|\n| 年化收益 | 38.32% | 38.27% | -0.05% |\n| 最大回撤 | 19.22% | 19.22% | 0% |\n| 夏普 | 1.562 | 1.557 | -0.005 |\n| 覆盖率 | - | 0.11% | - |\n\n### 说明\n\n- **覆盖率低**是因为 day1-3 是\"超跌反弹\"策略，只有满足超跌条件时才产生信号（非每日信号）\n- 融合效果略偏负，可能需要进一步调参或增加权重优化\n\n---\n\n**还有其他融合方向想测试吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":125542,"output":348,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":167298,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774098105227}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b6beca3","parentId":"53b80bf0","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:01:58.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 day1-3 融合进展汇报\n\n### 已完成\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 信号生成脚本 | ✅ `generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py` |\n| 历史因子数据 | ✅ **936行**，覆盖 **115只股票**（2024-01 ~ 2026-03） |\n| 融合配置 | ✅ `rd_agent_integration_day1_3.yaml` |\n| 融合回测 | ✅ 已执行 |\n\n### 回测结果对比\n\n| 指标 | 基础策略 | +day1-3融合 | 变化 |\n|------|----------|--------------|------|\n| 年化收益 | 38.32% | 38.27% | -0.05% |\n| 最大回撤 | 19.22% | 19.22% | 0% |\n| 夏普 | 1.562 | 1.557 | -0.005 |\n| 覆盖率 | - | 0.11% | - |\n\n### 说明\n\n- **覆盖率低**是因为 day1-3 是\"超跌反弹\"策略，只有满足超跌条件时才产生信号（非每日信号）\n- 融合效果略偏负，可能需要进一步调参或增加权重优化\n\n---\n\n**还有其他融合方向想测试吗？**"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774098118012}}
