{"type":"message","id":"c594154b","parentId":"1137eea7","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:14:46.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The analyzer service is failing due to API quota issues with Tavily. This is why the stock analyses are not being generated. The integration is in place, but it's failing due to external API limits.\n\nLet me explain this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"5bb44dab46680cd8fc7d04d61fd3ce6b130cf6338e9cabc29e0c7c6a87c5205e"},{"type":"text","text":"## ⚠️ 融合测试结果\n\n**个股分析功能已接入，但运行时遇到 API 配额问题：**\n\n```\n[Tavily] API Key: 配额已用尽\n[情报搜索] 搜索失败 - API 配额已用尽\n```\n\n### 融合链路是正常的\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `run_close_review_v1.py` | ✅ 可执行 |\n| `analyzer_service.analyze_stock()` | ✅ 可调用 |\n| API 配额 | ❌ Tavily 配额用尽 |\n\n### 原因\n- `daily_stock_analysis` 依赖 Tavily 做新闻搜索\n- 今日配额用尽，导致分析服务无法返回结果\n- **这不是融合代码的问题，是外部 API 配额限制**\n\n### 解决方案\n1. **升级 Tavily 套餐** - 增加 API 配额\n2. **换用其他搜索服务** - 如 Brave Search、DuckDuckGo\n3. **等待配额重置** - 通常次日恢复\n\n---\n\n**需要我帮你检查或配置其他搜索 API 吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":136492,"output":276,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":178176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774098868537}}
