{"type":"message","id":"10337347","parentId":"1ac84f5a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:25:26.836Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jk0uwegjhuoc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-21 工作日志\n\n## 今日完成事项\n\n### 1. day1-3 均值回归策略实现\n- 来源：小红书笔记 day1-3 项目（A股日频均值回归策略）\n- 目标：将该策略思想落地到 personal-a-share-research-system\n\n### 2. 产出文件\n| 类型 | 文件 |\n|------|------|\n| 配置文件 | `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/day1_3_mean_reversion.yaml` |\n| RD接入配置 | `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/rd_agent_integration_day1_3.yaml` |\n| 信号生成脚本 | `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py` |\n| Smoke test | 2026-03-10 日期，12只候选股，总仓位43.20% |\n\n### 3. 策略核心逻辑\n- **信号特征**：均线偏离(dist_ma10)、5日收益(ret5)、相对HS300超额收益(excess_ret5)、20日低位区间(range_pos20)\n- **市场门控**：strong/neutral/weak 三档动态仓位缩放\n- **接入方式**：生成 RD 因子 CSV，叠加到现有因子overlay回测链路\n\n### 4. Git Commit\n- Hash: `0e5a86d`\n- Message: \"feat(quant): add day1-3 mean reversion signal generator\"\n\n## 后续建议\n1. 收紧过滤条件（当前较宽松）\n2. Walk-Forward 验证策略稳健性\n3. 与现有策略做融合回测\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774099526829}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa3ee086","parentId":"10337347","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:25:48.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to append more content to today's memory about what was accomplished in the evening.","thinkingSignature":"82979a6f28d9ddc7ea4a895844208edd57ef78dd79c47c0d4ac07f586502b2fa"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0xyks1e1ysvz_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-21.md","oldText":"## 后续建议\n1. 收紧过滤条件（当前较宽松）\n2. Walk-Forward 验证策略稳健性\n3. 与现有策略做融合回测","newText":"## 后续建议\n1. 收紧过滤条件（当前较宽松）\n2. Walk-Forward 验证策略稳健性\n3. 与现有策略做融合回测\n\n---\n\n## 晚间进展 (21:00-21:25)\n\n### 5. day1-3 因子扩展到2年数据\n- 生成533个交易日因子数据（2024-01-02 ~ 2026-03-19）\n- 产出文件：\n  - `day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_2years.csv` (1101行，122只股票)\n  - 覆盖文件：533个单独日期文件\n- 融合回测结果：\n  - 覆盖率：0.11%（因子为超跌反弹信号，非每日信号）\n  - 年化收益变化：-0.05%（38.32% → 38.27%）\n\n### 6. daily_stock_analysis 融合状态\n- 状态：**已完成**（2026-03-19）\n- 三层融合架构：\n  1. 个股实时门禁：`stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py`\n  2. 盘前大盘复盘：`run_premarket_risk_v2.py`\n  3. 盘后个股分析：`run_close_review_v1.py`\n\n### 7. 个股分析功能实战测试\n- 测试股票：600519 贵州茅台\n- 结果：**成功输出完整分析报告**\n- 输出内容：\n  - 核心结论：🟢买入信号（缩量回踩MA5）\n  - 情绪得分：74\n  - 均线分析：MA5>MA10，但MA10与MA20粘合\n  - 作战计划：理想买点1445元，止损1420元，目标1500元\n  - 建议仓位：1-2成\n\n### 8. 用户新需求\n- 用户要求：直接发股票代码，输出完整专业分析报告\n- 当前限制：新闻搜索API（Tavily）配额用尽\n- 可用功能：技术分析（均线、成交量、K线形态、买卖点位）\n- 待解决：配置替代搜索API（BRAVE/BOCHA/SERPAPI）\n\n---\n\n## 待办\n- [ ] 配置替代搜索API以恢复新闻舆情分析\n- [ ] 优化day1-3融合权重提升收益\n- [ ] 用户股票分析实战"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":33453,"output":613,"cacheRead":41520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774099526837}}
