]:\n              - paragraph [ref=e155]: © 2014-2026\n              - paragraph [ref=e156]: 行吟信息科技（上海）有限公司\n              - paragraph [ref=e157]: 地址：上海市黄浦区马当路388号C座\n              - paragraph [ref=e158]: 电话：9501-3888\n      - generic [ref=e161]:\n        - generic [ref=e164]:\n          - generic [ref=e166]:\n            - img [ref=e170]\n            - img [ref=e174]\n            - img [ref=e178]\n            - img [ref=e182]\n          - generic [ref=e183]: 1/2\n          - img [ref=e186]\n          - img [ref=e190] [cursor=pointer]\n        - generic [ref=e197]:\n          - generic [ref=e199]:\n            - generic [ref=e200]:\n              - link [ref=e203] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/641b15d00000000011021978?channel_type=web_note_detail_r10&xsec_token=AB_J0nrm7a53x3bIrXR7m0buZmoVyMce_l-WA6fn1QCnU%3D&xsec_source=pc_note\n                - img [ref=e204]\n              - link \"mömö\" [ref=e205] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /user/profile/641b15d00000000011021978?channel_type=web_note_detail_r10&parent_page_channel_type=web_profile_board&xsec_token=AB_J0nrm7a53x3bIrXR7m0buZmoVyMce_l-WA6fn1QCnU=&xsec_source=pc_note\n                - generic [ref=e206]: mömö\n            - button \"关注\" [ref=e208] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - generic [ref=e210]: 关注\n          - generic [ref=e211]:\n            - generic [ref=e212]:\n              - generic [ref=e213]: 分享一个 OpenClaw 搜索工具的替代方案\n              - generic [ref=e215]:\n                - text: 今天发现 Tavily 额度用完了。我的 OpenClaw agent 每天要搜一堆东西（like论文、世界资讯、AI 行业动态），所以免费额度消耗得很快。Brave Search要绑支付方式，直接放弃。 然后想到：平时用 Claude Code CLI 和 Codex CLI，这两个不是自带 WebSearch Tool吗？干脆直接调用。 试了一下，完全可以： claude -p \"search the web for xxx\" --allowedTools \"WebSearch\" 这个能力作为 OpenClaw skill 可以直接从clawhub获取： 📦 claudecode-websearch 安装方式： clawhub install claudecode-websearch 装好之后跟 agent 说「search the web for xxx」就能用，结果质量很好，还带引用链接。 Codex CLI 也支持（有 --search flag）。 适用于有codex/claude订阅、不想再多为search付费的情况。\n                - link \"#OpenClaw\" [ref=e216] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=OpenClaw&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#AI工具\" [ref=e217] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=AI%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#claude\" [ref=e218] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=claude&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#claudecode\" [ref=e219] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=claudecode&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#codex\" [ref=e220] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=codex&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#效率工具\" [ref=e221] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#AI助手\" [ref=e222] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=AI%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%2589%258B&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#开发者选项\" [ref=e223] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=%25E5%25BC%2580%25E5%258F%2591%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2580%2589%25E9%25A1%25B9&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n                - link \"#vibecoding大赏\" [ref=e224] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /search_result?keyword=vibecoding%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B5%258F&type=54&source=web_note_detail_r10\n              - generic [ref=e225]:\n                - generic [ref=e226]: 编辑于 2天前 河北\n                - img [ref=e230] [cursor=pointer]\n            - generic [ref=e234]:\n              - img [ref=e235]\n              - paragraph [ref=e236]: 这是一片荒地点击评论\n          - generic [ref=e239]:\n            - generic [ref=e240]:\n              - generic [ref=e241]:\n                -