{"type":"message","id":"573de87d","parentId":"14b94826","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:37:18.066Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Codex 订阅过期了。让我检查一下当前可用的搜索方式。目前我们有：\n\n1. Tavily - 刚更新了 key，但需要等冷却结束（约1小时）\n2. Claude Code - 未安装\n3. Codex - 订阅过期\n4. Brave Search - 需要 API key\n5. 其他搜索 - 网络受限\n\n让我告诉用户当前状况。","thinkingSignature":"ab120879440b9e9febe66fe58b0ab263d0a2c454b719ef1f2418065524b1d8fa"},{"type":"text","text":"### 安装结果\n\n✅ **claudecode-websearch 已安装**\n\n但测试发现：\n- ❌ Claude Code CLI 未安装\n- ❌ Codex CLI 订阅已过期（`SUBSCRIPTION_NOT_FOUND`）\n\n---\n\n### 当前搜索状态\n\n| 搜索源 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| Tavily | ⏳ 冷却中（约1小时后可用）|\n| Claude Code | ❌ 未安装 |\n| Codex | ❌ 订阅过期 |\n| Brave | ❌ 需要 API Key |\n\n---\n\n**建议**：等1小时后 Tavily 配额恢复，或者你可以在 Claude Code/Codex 上续费订阅。\n\n要继续分析股票的话，当前技术分析功能是正常的，只是没有新闻舆情。需要我继续分析其他股票吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":53162,"output":236,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94806,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774100230226}}
{"type":"message","id":"6266e886","parentId":"573de87d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:37:18.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到了！这是一个关于 OpenClaw 搜索替代方案的笔记。\n\n### 核心内容\n\n| 项目 | 方案 |\n|------|------|\n| 问题 | Tavily 配额用完，Brave Search 要绑支付方式 |\n| 替代方案 | Claude Code / Codex CLI 自带 WebSearch |\n| 安装 | `clawhub install claudecode-websearch` |\n| 使用 | `claude -p \"search the web for xxx\" --allowedTools \"WebSearch\"` |\n\n让我安装试试："}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774100238678}}
