{"type":"message","id":"3d1ef23f","parentId":"25c26b12","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:56:13.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经创建了详细的集成路线图。让我给用户展示核心内容。","thinkingSignature":"df7a700cb08b86eb8597ef3e6dc9a23ea2a849abccf626681314c4fd5b3ae70a"},{"type":"text","text":"已生成详细路线图：📄 `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/docs/daily_stock_analysis_integration_roadmap.md`\n\n### 📋 集成规划\n\n| 阶段 | 功能 | 工时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Phase 1** | 统一调用入口 | 1-2天 |\n| **Phase 2** | Agent 问股 | 3-5天 |\n| **Phase 3** | 定时推送 | 2-3天 |\n| **Phase 4** | 图片识别/AI回测 | 5-7天 |\n\n### 🎯 优先级\n\n| 优先级 | 功能 |\n|--------|------|\n| P0 | 统一调用入口 |\n| P1 | Agent 问股 |\n| P2 | 定时推送 |\n| P3 | 图片识别 |\n| P4 | AI 回测验证 |\n\n---\n\n**你想从哪个开始？建议先做 P0 统一调用入口**，把现有的集成规范化，后续功能可以快速复用。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60115,"output":230,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101753,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774101351087}}
