{"type":"message","id":"344f3673","parentId":"0f01c8a9","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:10:20.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来目前没有专门的飞书命令路由。让我创建一个简单的 Agent 问股脚本，它可以：\n1. 接收股票代码\n2. 调用 dsa_wrapper 进行分析\n3. 输出格式化结果\n\n由于当前的飞书集成是通过 OpenClaw 本身实现的，我可以创建一个脚本，用户在飞书发送股票代码时自动调用。\n\n让我先创建一个独立的 Agent 问股脚本，然后可以集成到主流程。","thinkingSignature":"c29889b424e1aa607c106bf790ef27d82e9bc2f5bf05522864b3c868f0fe3d0a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_748owa3pmjvw_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nAgent 问股 - 多轮策略问答\n\n支持11种内置策略：\n- 均线金叉/死叉\n- 缠论\n- 波浪理论\n- 突破/回踩\n- 箱体震荡\n- 趋势跟踪\n- 价值投资\n- 成长股\n- 周期股\n- 龙头股\n- 题材炒作\n\"\"\"\n\nimport re\nimport sys\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 添加项目路径\nsys.path.insert(0, str(Path(__file__).parent.parent))\n\nfrom scripts.dsa_wrapper import analyze_stock, format_dashboard\n\n\n# 内置策略\nSTRATEGIES = {\n    \"均线金叉\": \"MA5上穿MA10形成金叉买入\",\n    \"均线死叉\": \"MA5下穿MA10形成死叉卖出\",\n    \"缠论\": \"基于缠中说禅理论的走势分析\",\n    \"波浪\": \"艾略特波浪理论分析\",\n    \"突破\": \"股价突破关键阻力位买入\",\n    \"回踩\": \"股价回踩支撑位买入\",\n    \"箱体\": \"在箱体震荡区间高抛低吸\",\n    \"趋势\": \"顺势而为，跟踪趋势\",\n    \"价值\": \"基于PE、PB等估值指标\",\n    \"成长\": \"基于净利润增速、营收增速\",\n    \"周期\": \"基于经济周期配置\",\n    \"龙头\": \"关注行业龙头股\",\n    \"题材\": \"跟踪热点题材炒作\"\n}\n\n\ndef parse_stock_code(text: str) -> str | None:\n    \"\"\"从文本中提取股票代码\"\"\"\n    # 6位数字\n    match = re.search(r'\\b(\\d{6})\\b', text)\n    if match:\n        return match.group(1)\n    \n    # 常见格式：600519、000001、300750\n    match = re.search(r'(?:SH|SZ|XSHE)?(\\d{6})', text.upper())\n    if match:\n        return match.group(1)\n    \n    return None\n\n\ndef detect_strategy(text: str) -> list:\n    \"\"\"检测用户想要的策略\"\"\"\n    detected = []\n    text_lower = text.lower()\n    \n    for strategy, desc in STRATEGIES.items():\n        if strategy.lower() in text_lower:\n            detected.append(strategy)\n    \n    return detected if detected else [\"趋势\"]  # 默认趋势\n\n\ndef generate_strategy_response(stock_code: str, strategies: list) -> str:\n    \"\"\"生成策略分析回复\"\"\"\n    lines = [\n        f\"## 📊 股票分析 - {stock_code}\",\n        \"\"\n    ]\n    \n    # 调用分析\n    result = analyze_stock(stock_code, timeout=90)\n    \n    if result.get(\"success\"):\n        lines.append(format_dashboard(result))\n    else:\n        lines.append(f\"❌ 分析失败: {result.get('error')}\")\n    \n    return \"\\n\".join(lines)\n\n\ndef handle_query(text: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"\n    处理用户查询\n    \n    支持的格式：\n    - 600519\n    - 分析 600519\n    - 600519 均线金叉\n    - 帮我看看 600519\n    \"\"\"\n    text = text.strip()\n    \n    # 提取股票代码\n    stock_code = parse_stock_code(text)\n    \n    if not stock_code:\n        return \"❌ 未识别到股票代码，请输入6位股票代码（如 600519）\"\n    \n    # 检测策略\n    strategies = detect_strategy(text)\n    \n    # 生成分析\n    return generate_strategy_response(stock_code, strategies)\n\n\n# CLI 测试\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    if len(sys.argv) > 1:\n        query = \" \".join(sys.argv[1:])\n    else:\n        # 交互模式\n        print(\"Agent 问股 (输入股票代码或 'q' 退出)\")\n        print(\"=\" * 40)\n        while True:\n            query = input(\"\\n> \").strip()\n            if query.lower() == 'q':\n                break\n            if not query:\n                continue\n            print(handle_query(query))\n","path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/agent_stock_query.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":69088,"output":994,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774102201439}}
