{"type":"message","id":"3e4072b6","parentId":"80fc8aca","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:12:05.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"P1 Agent 问股功能测试成功！现在让我总结一下完成的内容。","thinkingSignature":"ce6f04123366430b6949a8e6f500a74bc07dffc7dcdc6106e81df21a10e396a4"},{"type":"text","text":"### ✅ P1 Agent 问股 - 完成！\n\n**新增文件**：\n- `scripts/agent_stock_query.py` - Agent 问股主脚本\n- `scripts/feishu_stock_handler.py` - 飞书命令处理器\n\n**支持格式**：\n```\n600519\n600519 怎么样\n分析 600519\n帮我看看 300750\n```\n\n**测试结果**：\n```\n## 📊 贵州茅台(600519) 分析\n**建议**: 买入 | **置信度**: 中 | **情绪**: 74\n\n### 📈 关键数据\n- 收盘价: ¥1445.00\n- 涨跌幅: -0.54%\n- MA5: 1462.37\n...\n```\n\n---\n\n### 集成到飞书\n\n当用户在飞书发送股票代码时，会自动调用分析。需要配置 OpenClaw 路由。\n\n**下一步**：\n- P2: 定时推送配置\n- 或者现在可以直接用：`python3 scripts/feishu_stock_handler.py 600519`\n\n---\n\n**继续 P2 定时推送吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":72172,"output":245,"cacheRead":41408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113825,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774102317415}}
