{"type":"message","id":"c4b1c458","parentId":"f4af4f3a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:02:29.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"b9724941b6d6619d170dcfcf87d4f75da42cf187a4416417a7f41a93388286ba"},{"type":"text","text":"### ✅ P3 P4 全部完成！\n\n**新增文件**：\n\n| 功能 | 脚本 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **P3 图片识别** | `image_stock_extractor.py` | 从截图提取股票代码 |\n| **P4 AI回测** | `ai_backtest_verify.py` | 评估历史分析准确率 |\n\n---\n\n### 使用方式\n\n```bash\n# P3: 图片识别\npython3 scripts/image_stock_extractor.py /path/to/image.jpg\n\n# P4: AI 回测验证\npython3 scripts/ai_backtest_verify.py --days 30\n```\n\n---\n\n### 全部集成完成总结\n\n| 阶段 | 状态 | 文件 |\n|------|------|------|\n| P0 | ✅ | `dsa_wrapper.py` |\n| P1 | ✅ | `agent_stock_query.py`, `feishu_stock_handler.py` |\n| P2 | ✅ | `daily_stock_push.py` |\n| P3 | ✅ | `image_stock_extractor.py` |\n| P4 | ✅ | `ai_backtest_verify.py` |\n\n---\n\n**🎉 daily_stock_analysis 集成全部完成！**\n\n所有功能都已接入量化投研系统，你可以：\n- 直接发股票代码给我分析\n- 定时推送每日报告\n- 图片识别提取股票\n- 回测验证分析准确率"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":76209,"output":291,"cacheRead":39498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115998,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774105341903}}
