{"type":"message","id":"86bd1834","parentId":"7e481509","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:32:02.566Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ukqn47dfhavg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-21 工作日志\n\n## 今日完成事项\n\n### 1. day1-3 均值回归策略实现\n- 来源：小红书笔记 day1-3 项目（A股日频均值回归策略）\n- 目标：将该策略思想落地到 personal-a-share-research-system\n\n### 2. 产出文件\n| 类型 | 文件 |\n|------|------|\n| 配置文件 | `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/day1_3_mean_reversion.yaml` |\n| RD接入配置 | `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/rd_agent_integration_day1_3.yaml` |\n| 信号生成脚本 | `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py` |\n| Smoke test | 2026-03-10 日期，12只候选股，总仓位43.20% |\n\n### 3. 策略核心逻辑\n- **信号特征**：均线偏离(dist_ma10)、5日收益(ret5)、相对HS300超额收益(excess_ret5)、20日低位区间(range_pos20)\n- **市场门控**：strong/neutral/weak 三档动态仓位缩放\n- **接入方式**：生成 RD 因子 CSV，叠加到现有因子overlay回测链路\n\n### 4. Git Commit\n- Hash: `0e5a86d`\n- Message: \"feat(quant): add day1-3 mean reversion signal generator\"\n\n## 后续建议\n1. 收紧过滤条件（当前较宽松）\n2. Walk-Forward 验证策略稳健性\n3. 与现有策略做融合回测\n\n---\n\n## 晚间进展 (21:00-21:25)\n\n### 5. day1-3 因子扩展到2年数据\n- 生成533个交易日因子数据（2024-01-02 ~ 2026-03-19）\n- 产出文件：\n  - `day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_2years.csv` (1101行，122只股票)\n  - 覆盖文件：533个单独日期文件\n- 融合回测结果：\n  - 覆盖率：0.11%（因子为超跌反弹信号，非每日信号）\n  - 年化收益变化：-0.05%（38.32% → 38.27%）\n\n### 6. daily_stock_analysis 融合状态\n- 状态：**已完成**（2026-03-19）\n- 三层融合架构：\n  1. 个股实时门禁：`stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py`\n  2. 盘前大盘复盘：`run_premarket_risk_v2.py`\n  3. 盘后个股分析：`run_close_review_v1.py`\n\n\n[23 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774110722553}}
{"type":"message","id":"717a6963","parentId":"86bd1834","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:32:36.226Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我理解了记忆系统的格式：\n- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - 每日工作日志\n- 格式是 Markdown，包含日期标题和分类内容\n\n让我修改 Codex 记忆夜跑脚本，使其适配新的记忆系统，而不是同步到 Memos。","thinkingSignature":"059b519a53efceea6c7a2800a65876dedb3420b61be2cb2d0f0cd435e57f8697"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b1h81u4qe33q_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nCodex 记忆同步到 OpenClaw 记忆系统\n\n将 Codex 会话中的重要信息提取并保存到 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md 格式。\n\n当前记忆系统格式：\n- memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md - 每日工作日志\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport json\nimport argparse\nimport logging\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\nfrom zoneinfo import ZoneInfo\n\n# 配置\nHOME = Path(\"/Users/ling\")\nCODEX_HOME = HOME / \".codex\"\nWORKSPACE_DIR = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nMEMORY_DIR = WORKSPACE_DIR / \"memory\"\nSHANGHAI = ZoneInfo(\"Asia/Shanghai\")\n\nlogging.basicConfig(\n    level=logging.INFO,\n    format='%(asctime)s - %(levelname)s - %(message)s'\n)\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n\ndef get_today_date_str():\n    \"\"\"获取今日日期字符串\"\"\"\n    return datetime.now(SHANGHAI).strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n\ndef get_memory_file_path(date_str: str = None) -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取记忆文件路径\"\"\"\n    if date_str is None:\n        date_str = get_today_date_str()\n    return MEMORY_DIR / f\"{date_str}.md\"\n\n\ndef read_today_memory() -> str:\n    \"\"\"读取今日记忆\"\"\"\n    mem_file = get_memory_file_path()\n    if mem_file.exists():\n        return mem_file.read_text()\n    return \"\"\n\n\ndef append_to_memory(section_title: str, content: str):\n    \"\"\"追加内容到今日记忆\"\"\"\n    mem_file = get_memory_file_path()\n    \n    # 读取现有内容\n    existing = \"\"\n    if mem_file.exists():\n        existing = mem_file.read_text()\n    \n    # 检查是否已存在该部分\n    if f\"## {section_title}\" in existing:\n        logger.info(f\"Section '{section_title}' already exists, skipping\")\n        return\n    \n    # 追加新部分\n    new_content = f\"\\n\\n---\\n\\n## {section_title}\\n\\n{content}\\n\"\n    \n    if existing:\n        # 追加到文件\n        with open(mem_file, \"a\") as f:\n            f.write(new_content)\n    else:\n        # 创建新文件\n        header = f\"# {get_today_date_str()} 工作日志\\n\"\n        with open(mem_file, \"w\") as f:\n            f.write(header + new_content)\n    \n    logger.info(f\"Appended to {mem_file}\")\n\n\ndef extract_codex_sessions():\n    \"\"\"提取 Codex 会话\"\"\"\n    sessions_dir = CODEX_HOME / \"sessions\"\n    \n    if not sessions_dir.exists():\n        logger.warning(f\"Codex sessions dir not found: {sessions_dir}\")\n        return []\n    \n    sessions = []\n    today = datetime.now(SHANGHAI).date()\n    \n    for session_file in sessions_dir.glob(\"*.json\"):\n        try:\n            # 读取会话文件\n            data = json.loads(session_file.read_text())\n            \n            # 检查是否是今日会话\n            if \"created_at\" in data:\n                created = datetime.fromisoformat(data[\"created_at\"].replace(\"Z\", \"+00:00\"))\n                if created.date() == today:\n                    sessions.append(data)\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.debug(f\"Skip {session_file.name}: {e}\")\n    \n    logger.info(f\"Found {len(sessions)} Codex sessions for today\")\n    return sessions\n\n\ndef extract_key_info(sessions: list) -> list:\n    \"\"\"从会话中提取关键信息\"\"\"\n    key_info = []\n    \n    for session in sessions:\n        # 提取用户请求和助手响应中的关键信息\n        messages = session.get(\"messages\", [])\n        \n        for msg in messages:\n            role = msg.get(\"role\", \"\")\n            content = msg.get(\"content\", \"\")\n            \n            if role == \"user\" and content:\n                # 提取用户请求\n                if any(kw in content for kw in [\"需要\", \"要\", \"帮我\", \"分析\", \"做\"]):\n                    key_info.append({\n                        \"type\": \"user_request\",\n                        \"content\": content[:200]  # 截取前200字符\n                    })\n    \n    return key_info\n\n\ndef run_nightly():\n    \"\"\"夜跑主函数\"\"\"\n    logger.info(\"=== Codex Memory Nightly ===\")\n    \n    # 提取今日 Codex 会话\n    sessions = extract_codex_sessions()\n    \n    if not sessions:\n        logger.info(\"No Codex sessions found today\")\n        return\n    \n    # 提取关键信息\n    key_info = extract_key_info(sessions)\n    \n    if key_info:\n        # 格式化内容\n        content_lines = []\n        for info in key_info:\n            content_lines.append(f\"- **{info['type']}**: {info['content']}\")\n        \n        content = \"\\n\".join(content_lines)\n        \n        # 追加到今日记忆\n        append_to_memory(\"Codex 会话提取\", content)\n        \n        logger.info(f\"Extracted {len(key_info)} items from Codex sessions\")\n    else:\n        logger.info(\"No key info found in sessions\")\n\n\ndef run_fast_sync():\n    \"\"\"快速同步\"\"\"\n    run_nightly()\n\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Codex Memory Sync\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"mode\", nargs=\"?\", default=\"run-nightly\", \n                       choices=[\"run-nightly\", \"run-fast\"])\n    parser.add_argument(\"--date\", help=\"Specific date (YYYY-MM-DD)\")\n    \n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    \n    if args.mode == \"run-nightly\":\n        run_nightly()\n    elif args.mode == \"run-fast\":\n        run_fast_sync()\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n","path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/bridge_codex_to_memory.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":88013,"output":1305,"cacheRead":37741,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774110722569}}
