{"type":"message","id":"d82b84f8","parentId":"f7d6a3e5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:33:48.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问是否还需要使用 Memos 和 Docker。让我解释一下当前的情况。","thinkingSignature":"be424307cb8ebac83bd3a79851075f93b5147b6b8ba7f23acc4ddf7b61f48b7a"},{"type":"text","text":"**是的，新方案不需要 Memos 和 Docker 了！**\n\n### 对比\n\n| 组件 | 旧方案 | 新方案 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| Memos | ❌ 需要（常驻运行） | ✅ 不需要 |\n| Docker | ❌ 需要 | ✅ 不需要 |\n| 存储 | Memos 数据库 | `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` |\n| 依赖 | memos_primary_pipeline | 纯 Python |\n\n### 新方案优势\n\n1. **更简单** - 直接写 Markdown 文件\n2. **更稳定** - 不依赖外部服务\n3. **更兼容** - 与 OpenClaw 记忆系统无缝集成\n\n### 你的记忆系统\n\n```\nmemory/\n├── 2026-03-21.md   ← 今日工作日志\n├── 2026-03-20.md\n├── ...\n└── MEMORY.md        ← 长期记忆\n```\n\n---\n\n**Memos 和 Docker 可以停掉了**，需要我帮你清理相关配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":125,"output":223,"cacheRead":37741,"cacheWrite":89971,"totalTokens":128060,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774110807568}}
