{"type":"message","id":"b9caa051","parentId":"59ccb5b4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:35:03.440Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9elurb1nhg9q_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - 统一记忆\n\n这里存放跨渠道、跨会话都值得长期保留的事实与铁律；不放临时任务进度，不放一次性过程。\n\n## 关于张玲\n- 用户名：张玲\n- 主要沟通渠道：飞书 DM\n- 核心关注：量化投资、A股研究、自动化执行链路\n\n## 助手分工\n- 周到：健身/生活类提醒与消息\n- 来福来财：量化投资、回测、盘前检查、策略报告\n\n## 长期执行铁律\n- 当用户说“继续任务 / 我要看报告 / 先给结果 / 现在执行”时，先执行并先给验收件，不要反问阻塞。\n- 非交易日 / 非交易时段，不给“可执行买价”；只给预算、优先级、开盘触发条件。\n- 安装任何新 skill 前，必须先做 `clawsec` 安全检查。\n- 任务完成后要第一时间汇报结果，不能只报“正在处理”。\n- 任何明确有利于量化系统和投研组织的事项，默认自动推进，不再额外征求确认；仅在外发、破坏性操作、权限边界、真实资金/实盘执行、公共发言、账号密钥等高风险场景暂停确认。\n- 所有面向张玲直接展示的内容必须默认使用中文，包括飞书消息、交互卡片、网页面板标题/按钮/标签/说明；英文仅保留在文件名、路径、代码与内部字段，不直接作为对张玲的展示文案。\n- 量化系统凡输出“买入推荐 / 候选股 / 优先股 / 可开仓列表”，必须先经过当日实时大盘与个股实时确认：先看盘中指数、盘中市场宽度、个股实时涨跌、数据异常、AI 实时决策，再决定是否给出推荐；禁止用昨日收盘口径或早盘旧快照支撑当日盘中买入推荐。\n\n## 量化系统当前稳定结论\n- 主项目：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system`\n- 当前已沉淀的稳定策略口径之一：Qlib breadth + turnover hardcap relaxed\n  - 年化：55.07%\n  - 最大回撤：24.89%\n  - 夏普：2.794\n  - 状态：`robust_pass=true`\n- 盘前强检已自动化：交易日 `09:20-09:40` 自动执行 strict precheck\n- 每日策略审计已自动化：自动输出 md/json 报告\n- 实盘总览面板已自动化：支持生成 dashboard 并推送飞书摘要\n\n## 当前资金与口径\n- 当前总资金量：93万\n- 实盘当前可用资金：18万\n- 模拟盘口径：按 100 万可用资金计算（三个账户合计日增上限=100万）；当前若无买入，则按 100 万可用资金处理\n- 三模拟盘日增上限：防御盘=16.7万/日，平衡盘=33.3万/日，进取盘=50万/日，合计≤100万\n\n## 环境与系统\n- GitHub 仓库：`seablue1985/openclaw-config`\n- self-improving agent：已启用（自动学习、自动日报、自动规则提升、半自动技能草稿）\n- `openclaw-workspace` skill：已安装，可用于 workspace 审计与瘦身\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774110903428}}
{"type":"message","id":"f44ba90d","parentId":"b9caa051","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:35:30.178Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了。MEMORY.md 是长期记忆的核心，包含铁律和重要结论。但是确实有一些问题：\n\n1. **上下文限制** - 每次会话只能读取有限的内容2. **长期积累** - 多年后文件会很大\n\n解决方案：\n1. **定期整理** - 每周/月将重要信息提炼到 MEMORY.md\n2. **清理过期** - 删除/归档旧的 memory 文件3. **语义检索** - 用 memory_search 工具搜索（如果有的话）\n\n让我给用户解释并提供解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"d704960cb7dddba9cf9f3276e89b91661c7ea45a186a5e24df29ca4938c4e7a9"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！OpenClaw 有机制，但需要配合整理：\n\n### 当前记忆机制\n\n| 文件 | 用途 | 加载方式 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| `MEMORY.md` | 长期铁律/核心结论 | 每次启动读取 |\n| `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` | 每日工作日志 | 需要时读取 |\n\n### 潜在问题\n\n1. **上下文有限** - 只能读取部分内容\n2. **文件会变大** - 几年后可能很大\n\n---\n\n### 解决方案\n\n我建议加一个**定期整理机制**：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g4v13rhv9635_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n记忆系统整理脚本\n\n功能：\n1. 将重要信息提炼到 MEMORY.md\n2. 清理过期的 daily memory\n3. 生成记忆索引\n\n使用方式：\n# 每周整理\npython3 scripts/organize_memory.py --weekly\n\n# 每月整理\npython3 scripts/organize_memory.py --monthly\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport json\nimport argparse\nimport logging\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom collections import defaultdict\n\n# 配置\nWORKSPACE_DIR = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\")\nMEMORY_DIR = WORKSPACE_DIR / \"memory\"\nMEMORY_FILE = WORKSPACE_DIR / \"MEMORY.md\"\n\nlogging.basicConfig(\n    level=logging.INFO,\n    format='%(asctime)s - %(levelname)s - %(message)s'\n)\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n\ndef get_memory_files(days: int = 30) -> list:\n    \"\"\"获取最近的 memory 文件\"\"\"\n    files = []\n    for f in MEMORY_DIR.glob(\"*.md\"):\n        if f.name in [\"MEMORY.md\"]:\n            continue\n        # 只处理 YYYY-MM-DD 格式\n        if len(f.stem) == 10 and \"-\" in f.stem:\n            files.append(f)\n    return sorted(files, key=lambda x: x.name, reverse=True)[:days]\n\n\ndef extract_key_points(content: str) -> list:\n    \"\"\"提取关键点\"\"\"\n    key_points = []\n    \n    # 提取带 ✅ 或 ❌ 的行\n    for line in content.split(\"\\n\"):\n        if \"✅\" in line or \"❌\" in line or \"已完成\" in line or \"完成\" in line:\n            # 简化\n            point = line.strip()\n            if len(point) > 5:\n                key_points.append(point[:100])\n    \n    return key_points[:5]  # 最多5条\n\n\ndef summarize_daily_memory(files: list) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"汇总每日记忆\"\"\"\n    summary = defaultdict(list)\n    \n    for f in files:\n        try:\n            content = f.read_text()\n            date = f.stem\n            \n            # 提取关键点\n            points = extract_key_points(content)\n            if points:\n                summary[date] = points\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.debug(f\"Skip {f.name}: {e}\")\n    \n    return summary\n\n\ndef update_memory_file(summary: dict):\n    \"\"\"更新 MEMORY.md\"\"\"\n    # 读取现有内容\n    existing = \"\"\n    if MEMORY_FILE.exists():\n        existing = MEMORY_FILE.read_text()\n    \n    # 添加整理记录\n    new_section = f\"\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 记忆整理 ({datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')})\\n\"\n    new_section += \"### 近期重要事项\\n\"\n    \n    for date, points in sorted(summary.items(), reverse=True):\n        new_section += f\"\\n#### {date}\\n\"\n        for p in points:\n            new_section += f\"- {p}\\n\"\n    \n    # 添加到文件\n    with open(MEMORY_FILE, \"a\") as f:\n        f.write(new_section)\n    \n    logger.info(f\"Updated {MEMORY_FILE}\")\n\n\ndef archive_old_memories(files: list, months: int = 3):\n    \"\"\"归档旧记忆\"\"\"\n    archive_dir = MEMORY_DIR / \"archive\"\n    archive_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\n    \n    cutoff = datetime.now() - timedelta(days=months * 30)\n    \n    archived = 0\n    for f in files:\n        try:\n            # 解析日期\n            date_str = f.stem\n            file_date = datetime.strptime(date_str, \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n            \n            if file_date < cutoff:\n                # 移动到归档目录\n                dest = archive_dir / f.name\n                f.rename(dest)\n                archived += 1\n                logger.info(f\"Archived: {f.name}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.debug(f\"Skip {f.name}: {e}\")\n    \n    logger.info(f\"Archived {archived} files\")\n\n\ndef generate_index(files: list) -> str:\n    \"\"\"生成索引\"\"\"\n    lines = [\"# 记忆索引\\n\"]\n    lines.append(f\"生成时间: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')}\\n\")\n    lines.append(f\"总文件数: {len(files)}\\n\")\n    lines.append(\"\\n## 文件列表\\n\")\n    \n    for f in files:\n        lines.append(f\"- {f.name}\")\n    \n    return \"\\n\".join(lines)\n\n\ndef run_weekly():\n    \"\"\"每周整理\"\"\"\n    logger.info(\"=== Weekly Memory Organization ===\")\n    \n    # 获取过去7天\n    files = get_memory_files(7)\n    \n    # 汇总\n    summary = summarize_daily_memory(files)\n    \n    if summary:\n        # 更新 MEMORY.md\n        update_memory_file(summary)\n    \n    logger.info(f\"Processed {len(files)} files\")\n\n\ndef run_monthly():\n    \"\"\"每月整理\"\"\"\n    logger.info(\"=== Monthly Memory Organization ===\")\n    \n    # 获取过去30天\n    files = get_memory_memory(30)\n    \n    # 汇总\n    summary = summarize_daily_memory(files)\n    \n    if summary:\n        update_memory_file(summary)\n    \n    # 归档3个月前的\n    archive_old_memories(files, months=3)\n    \n    # 生成索引\n    index = generate_index(files)\n    index_file = MEMORY_DIR / \"memory_index.md\"\n    index_file.write_text(index)\n    \n    logger.info(f\"Processed {len(files)} files\")\n\n\ndef main():\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Memory Organization\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--weekly\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"Weekly organization\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--monthly\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"Monthly organization\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--days\", type=int, default=30, help=\"Number of days to process\")\n    \n    args = parser.parse_args()\n    \n    if args.weekly:\n        run_weekly()\n    elif args.monthly:\n        run_monthly()\n    else:\n        # 默认处理指定天数\n        files = get_memory_files(args.days)\n        summary = summarize_daily_memory(files)\n        logger.info(f\"Found {len(summary)} days with content\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n","path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/organize_memory.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":92286,"output":1611,"cacheRead":37741,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774110903441}}
