{"type":"message","id":"35f6be8d","parentId":"6c8c5d03","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:35:48.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，让我给用户解释一下解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"fcc58802fc4e14c7aa7e3fc66ff8871cdcbc1bb977f7257c9afe37486f2c0757"},{"type":"text","text":"### ✅ 已添加整理机制\n\n**新脚本**：`scripts/organize_memory.py`\n\n```bash\n# 每周整理（提取要点到 MEMORY.md）\npython3 scripts/organize_memory.py --weekly\n\n# 每月整理（+ 归档旧文件 + 生成索引）\npython3 scripts/organize_memory.py --monthly\n```\n\n### 机制说明\n\n| 操作 | 频率 | 内容 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 提取要点 | 每周 | 把重要事项写入 MEMORY.md |\n| 归档 | 每月 | 3个月前的移至 archive/ |\n| 索引 | 每月 | 生成 memory_index.md |\n\n### 这样就不会丢失了\n\n- **短期** → `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- **长期** → `MEMORY.md`（每次启动都读）\n- **索引** → `memory_index.md`（快速检索）\n\n需要我把这个加到定时任务里吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":94048,"output":204,"cacheRead":37741,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774110934981}}
